---
title: leaguebot
description: Discord bot that retrieves stats from the Riot API
repository: taeyeong2k/leaguebot
url: https://github.com/taeyeong2k/leaguebot
date: 2023-12-1
published: true
---

Discord bot for a personal project which retrieves stats from the Riot API. Functions include checking in-game account information, registering an in-game account to a discord identity, retrieving match information and more.